summary: so you know how phil tells fans who have self harm scars or are shaking from anxiety that nothing can hurt them unless they let...
body:
so you know how phil tells fans who have self harm scars or are shaking from anxiety that nothing can hurt them unless they let it and then embraces them for a good long period in the sweetest way possible?

well don’t think about him doing that similarity to dan when dans sad or has low energy or has an existential crisis or has no self esteem in which he inevitably doubts his self worth.


phil lester is too good for this universe.
